descriptionHtml:
[heading][font=verdana]DESCRIPTION[/heading]
Brown dog with a white nose and white socks :)
To replace vigilance (and I think all pet dogs because they\'re the same apparently?)
I wanted a dog that\'s got some soul to him. This is a heros dog right here! :d

[heading]UPDATE HISTORY[/heading]
Update 1.3 : Updated normal map for a healthier, shinier coat
Update 1.2 : Fixed seaming issue
Update 1.1 : Darkened brown

[heading]INSTALLATION[/heading]
Unpack .rar contents to Data\\

Check out the [url=http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=2250]black version here[/url]
